{"title":"造船谣","authors":["宁宇"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":3,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"造船谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁宇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回答"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你问哪种人最美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电焊姑娘最美。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀登插天的桅杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云像纱巾在肩上飘飞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸似红日一轮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腰如弯弓欲射，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只见她手儿一挥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一蓬兰花迎风纷飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你问哪种人最美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装配工人最美。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍立青钢色甲板，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天如幕广阔深邃；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴筋胳膊高举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抡动八磅大锤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一锤一个鼓点哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲出喜报满天翻飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你问哪种人最美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们休息时最美。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解衣袒胸，把帽子后推，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"痛饮沁人肺腑的冰水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑谈竞赛成绩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人喜似同酒醉……，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤胆忠心搞建设，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造船工，人美心更美！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳在头上升降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮在身旁旋转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢板踩在我们脚下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青天当做天花板。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造船工人的家啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是万吨钢船的摇篮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银亮的下水滑轨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是通向蓝色海洋的门槛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们用鎯头的语言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和新船钢板交谈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们用电花的针线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缝制世界最大的衣衫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但有时也争吵心焦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为一只铆钉一寸钢板；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们拿船只的吨位，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把对祖国的爱情计算！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊邃［suì］　沁［qìn］"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}